    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 requirements. Grid convergence index values are within acceptance bounds, PIV validation errors are consistent with published inter-laboratory variability, and the relative hemolysis index predictions fall within experimental scatter for all 5 assessed operating points. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device hemolysis assessment.",
